# Privacy Policy

Indie Revenue Dashboard is a Chrome extension designed to help indie developers view revenue analytics from services such as Stripe directly inside their browser.

## Data Collection

This extension does not collect, store, or transmit personal user data to any external servers operated by the developer.

## Local Storage

User configuration such as API keys and preferences are stored locally using Chrome's `chrome.storage.local` API.

This data remains on the user's device and is only used by the extension to communicate directly with provider APIs such as Stripe.

## External Requests

The extension may send requests directly from the user's browser to third-party APIs (such as Stripe) using credentials provided by the user.

No data is transmitted to servers operated by the developer.

## Data Sharing

This extension does not sell, transfer, or share user data with third parties.

## Contact

If you have questions about this privacy policy you can contact us at hello@andoware.com
